  <model name="ImplementingSTEEPMethodology-Step1" desc="The first stage in implementing the STEEP methodology addresses the codependence of deciding the transformational goal and enrolling the stakeholders. The scope is thus defined by the setting of system boundary. Crucial to making this happen and for the subsequent steps in implementation is the need to animate the process. At this stage before anything has started we know that the &lt;Animating the methodology&gt; process is not performing well [0.0, 0.0]. Also we know nothing about the system boundary [0.0, 1.0]. Necessity valaues have been set to 1.0, we can be categorical about non-performance at this stage. " learningRate="1.0" necessityPower="1.0" propagationAlgorithm="Juniper" normalizationMethod="Yager's Method" pairwiseCombinationMethod="Minimum of pairs" />
